English: Compilation of pictures of renowned Argentines from 19th, 20th and 21st Centuries:

  • 19th century politics: Jose de San Martín, Manuel Belgrano, Mariano Moreno, Domingo F. Sarmiento, Juan Manuel de Rosas, María Sánchez de Thompson, Leandro N. Alem.
  • 20th, 21st century politics: Eva Perón, Che Guevara, Juan Perón, Arturo Illia, Hipólito Yrigoyen, Raul Alfonsín, Nestor Kirchner.
  • Pop culture, journalism: Alberto Olmedo, Carlos Gardel, Mercedes Sosa, Charly Garcia, Susana Giménez, Sandro de America, Tita Merello.
  • Arts and Science: Ernesto Sabato, Bernardo Houssay, Jorge Luis Borges, Luis Leloir, Lola Mora, Rene Favaloro, Julio Cortazar.
  • Sports: Diego Armando Maradona, Juan Manuel Fangio, Emanuel Ginobilli, Luciana Aymar, Lionel Messi, Gabriela Sabatini, Gabriel Batistuta.
